hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition.name: MailBodyMessage
hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition.description: Mail body message to descript the build list

hudson.tasks.BatchFile.command:
ECHO Changing directory to: %CLEANUP_SCRIPT_LOCATION% Set Debug_Flag="" IF "%Debug%" EQU "true" SET Debug_Flag="--debug" cd /d %CLEANUP_SCRIPT_LOCATION%
ECHO. ECHO. ECHO. ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning Archer Build Outputs - Started +++++++++++++++++++++ py cleanup.py -p %ARCHER_BUILDS_URL% -r UOMD_[1-9][6-9].*.*.[1-2]*00_Release --keeplast 4 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --html "Archer Build Outputs (Release)" --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR py cleanup.py -p %ARCHER_BUILDS_URL% -r UOMD_[1-9][6-9].*.*.[1-2]*00_Debug --keeplast 4 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --html "Archer Build Outputs (Debug)" --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning Archer Build Outputs - Done +++++++++++++++++++++ ECHO. ECHO. ECHO. ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning Personal uArcher Build Outputs - Started +++++++++++++++++++++ py cleanup.py -p %ARCHER_TASKS_BUILDS_URL% -r *_Release --olderthan 7d --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --html "uArcher Personal Build Outputs (Release)" --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR py cleanup.py -p %ARCHER_TASKS_BUILDS_URL% -r *_Debug --olderthan 7d --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --html "uArcher Personal Build Outputs (Debug)" --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning Personal uArcher Build Outputs - Done +++++++++++++++++++++ ECHO. ECHO. ECHO. ::ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning CodeViews - Started +++++++++++++++++++++ ::py cleanup.py -p %CODEVIEW_URL% -r UOMD_BLD_[1-9][6-9].*.*.[1-2]*00_code --keeplast 10 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% ::%Debug_Flag% --html "Code View" --excludesPattern KEEP* ::if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR ::ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning CodeViews - Done +++++++++++++++++++++ ECHO. ECHO. ECHO. ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning Archer SCHEDULED Build Outputs and Installers - Started +++++++++++++++++++++ py cleanup.py -p %ARCHER_SCHEDULED_BUILDS_URL% -r *_Release --keeplast 1 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR py cleanup.py -p %ARCHER_SCHEDULED_BUILDS_URL% -r *_Debug --keeplast 1 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR py cleanup.py -p %ARCHER_SCHEDULED_INSTALLERS_URL% -r Archer_Installation* --keeplast 1 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning Archer SCHEDULED Build Outputs - Done +++++++++++++++++++++ ECHO. ECHO. ECHO. ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning RDM Build Outputs - Started +++++++++++++++++++++ py cleanup.py -p %RDM_BUILDS_URL% -r RDM_[1-9][6-9].*.*.[1-2]*00_Release --keeplast 4 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --html "RDM Build Outputs (Release)" --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR py cleanup.py -p %RDM_BUILDS_URL% -r RDM_[1-9][6-9].*.*.[1-2]*00_Debug --keeplast 4 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --html "RDM Build Outputs (Debug)" --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR --html "RDM Build Outputs (Debug)" ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning RDM Build Outputs - Done +++++++++++++++++++++ ECHO. ECHO. ECHO. ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning RDM SCHEDULED Build Outputs and Installers - Started +++++++++++++++++++++ py cleanup.py -p %RDM_SCHEDULED_BUILDS_URL% -r RDM_*_Release --keeplast 1 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR py cleanup.py -p %RDM_SCHEDULED_BUILDS_URL% -r RDM_*_Debug --keeplast 1 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR py cleanup.py -p %RDM_SCHEDULED_INSTALLERS_URL% -r RDM_* --keeplast 1 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR py cleanup.py -p %BLOSSOM_SCHEDULED_INSTALLERS_URL% -r TDD_* --keeplast 1 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning RDM SCHEDULED Build Outputs - Done +++++++++++++++++++++ ECHO. ECHO. ECHO. ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning ARCHER/RDM/BLOSSOM Installers - Started +++++++++++++++++++++ py cleanup.py -p %ARCHER_INSTALLERS_URL% -r Archer_Installation_[1-9][6-9].*.*.[1-2]*00 --keeplast 4 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --html "Archer Installers" --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR py cleanup.py -p %RDM_INSTALLERS_URL% -r RDM_[1-9][6-9].*.*.[1-2]*00 --keeplast 4 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --html "RDM Installers" --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR py cleanup.py -p %BLOSSOM_INSTALLERS_URL% -r TDD_[1-9][6-9].*.*.[1-2]*00 --keeplast 4 --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --html "Blossom Installers" --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning ARCHER/RDM/BLOSSOM Installers - Done +++++++++++++++++++++ ECHO. ECHO. ECHO. ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning Personal RDM Build Outputs - Started +++++++++++++++++++++ py cleanup.py -p %RDM_TASKS_BUILDS_URL% -r *_Release --olderthan 7d --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --html "RDM Personal Build Outputs (Release)" --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR py cleanup.py -p %RDM_TASKS_BUILDS_URL% -r *_Debug --olderthan 7d --action=%CLEANUP_ACTION% --excludesFile=%EXCLUDES_FILE% %Debug_Flag% --html "RDM Personal Build Outputs (Debug)" --excludesPattern KEEP* if %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 GOTO ERROR ECHO +++++++++++++++++++++ Cleanning Personal RDM Build Outputs - Done +++++++++++++++++++++ GOTO END
:ERROR ECHO ============================================= ECHO Cleanup Execution Failed ECHO ============================================= Exit /b 1
:END ECHO ============================================= ECHO Cleanup Execution Completed Successfully ECHO =============================================

hudson.plugins.emailext.ExtendedEmailPub.defaultSubject: OMD Folder Automatic Cleanup Report [${ENV, var="MailSubjectPrefix"}] - ${ENV, var="BUILD_TIMESTAMP"}
hudson.plugins.emailext.ExtendedEmailPub.defaultContent:
Dear User

Following are list of the Builds/Installers/CodeViews ${ENV, var="MailBodyMessage"}
Please note that builds are sorted from the newest to the oldest build (per version)
${ENV,var="MailAlertMessage"} For any issue please contact CM team.

${FILE,path="C:/Temp/cleanup_html_mail.html"}
Regards
OMD CM Team
